{"ID":"20220619170656-r4jwa9z","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220619170656-r4jwa9z","title":"LeetCode Problem","type":"doc","updated":"20220620104518"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220619170947-48qwksr","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-48qwksr","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何判断二维数组是否为空？"}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-ci2llu6","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-ci2llu6","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220619170947-mnnp3ky","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-mnnp3ky","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有三点要注意："}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-yy87bou","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-yy87bou","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1.数组首地址是否为空"}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-sefsqfo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-sefsqfo","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2.是否为{}，也就是array.length==0的情况"}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-cadbe0t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-cadbe0t","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3.{{}}，这时array.length=1，但是array[0].length==0。满足任意一个条件就可以返回false了。"}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-fi87sce","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-fi87sce","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"即以下为判断方法："}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-tyrigft","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-tyrigft","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"if(array==null||array.length==0||(array.length==1\u0026amp;\u0026amp;array[0].length==0)) return false;"}]}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-1ie99z1","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-1ie99z1","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"String和StringBuilder"}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-6h8b85x","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"fold":"0","id":"20220619170947-6h8b85x","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220619170947-ncsfqib","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-ncsfqib","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尽管StringBuilder和String都表示字符序列，但它们的实现方式不同。String是不可变的类型。也就是说，每个看似修改String对象的操作实际上都会创建一个新字符串。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-d4uocdk","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-d4uocdk","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder(\"ABC\", 50);\n\n// Append three characters (D, E, and F) to the end of the StringBuilder.\nsb.Append(new char[] { 'D', 'E', 'F' });\n\n// Append a format string to the end of the StringBuilder.\nsb.AppendFormat(\"GHI{0}{1}\", 'J', 'k');\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-rwgem0h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-rwgem0h","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"charAt（）"}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-hurtooi","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-hurtooi","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220619170947-dldgns3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-dldgns3","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"charAt() 方法用于返回指定索引处的字符。索引范围为从 0 到 length() - 1。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-g6062ss","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-g6062ss","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"public class Test {\n    public static void main(String args[]) {\n        String s = \"www.runoob.com\";\n        char result = s.charAt(6);\n        System.out.println(result);\n    }\n}\n以上程序执行结果为：\n\nn\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-4pnh0zp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-4pnh0zp","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"单引号和双引号的区别"}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-tib358v","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-tib358v","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220619170947-h2rxvki","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-h2rxvki","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"区别1：java中的单引号表示字符，java中的双引号是字符串。"}]},{"ID":"20220619170947-sm5h5ii","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220619170947-sm5h5ii","updated":"20220619170947"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"区别2：单引号引的数据一般是char类型的；双引号引的数据 是String类型的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220619171419-ed7sp3c","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220619171419-ed7sp3c","updated":"20220620104142"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"二叉树"}]},{"ID":"20220620104206-oe8ccqa","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220620104206-oe8ccqa","updated":"20220620104518"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220620104231-1rwil6p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220620104231-1rwil6p","updated":"20220620104317"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前序遍历："}]},{"ID":"20220620104402-wdnbusq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220620104402-wdnbusq","updated":"20220620104427"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"image.png"},{"Type":"NodeC